responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "634506194EF3AB60000E0992E3A5D609", "Entry #238 The days are gone. Our ambitions and dreams have become the dust and grime beneath goblin fingernails. And if I see another goblin I\'ll puke. Then, I\'ll wake up from my nightmare and puke again. They\'ve sent us here to suffer. Lone rangers in an inhospitable world. Only Roland continues to say his morning prayers like a prattling idiot. ")
